node.text:
iOS 14.7.1 vs iOS 14.7
🔋 𝗕𝗮𝘁𝘁𝗲𝗿𝘆 𝗹𝗶𝗳𝗲: increased with 1.94%.
⏱ 𝗣𝗲𝗿𝗳𝗼𝗿𝗺𝗮𝗻𝗰𝗲: decreased with 0.19%, so almost no changes in performance.
These results are averages, so they may vary on each device.
